Hey guys,

My long period as a hermit to this group is over. I return from the wilderness with a rather old book in the alphabet we all use and love. I have the file hosted at Transfering the WEB into the Quikscript alphabet.
Transfering the WEB into the Quikscript alphabet.
Transfering the WEB into the Quikscript alphabet.
View on sourceforge.net
Preview by Yahoo

 

and will have printed editions available soon. If you don't like the restored names, feel free to clone the code repository because I am creatively exhausted and open sources are awesome.

Enjoy!
